Title: A Green Who Can't Sleep?
Description:
$n... we have a problem.

Posidriss has insomnia.

I did not even know it was possible for a green dragon to not be able to fall asleep! How are they to learn to protect the Dream if they cannot enter it?

Please, try anything you can think of to help Posidriss fall asleep.
ObjectivesText: Try to help Posidriss fall asleep.
CompletionText: Every green dragon needs to be able to sleep!
RewardText: We uh... we will keep working on it. We have to!
